<article class="mb-5">
    <h3>How the Dynamic Layout System Works</h3>
    <p>
        The system automatically discovers all <code>.ejs</code> files in the <code>views/layouts/</code> directory and makes them available for use.
    </p>
    
    <h5>Available Layouts:</h5>
    <ul>
        <li><strong>homepage</strong> - Main website layout with navigation and footer</li>
        <li><strong>admin</strong> - Admin panel layout with sidebar</li>
        <li><strong>blog</strong> - Blog layout with sidebar and blog-specific styling</li>
    </ul>
    
    <p>
        Each route can specify which layout to use, or the system will fall back to the default layout.
    </p>
</article>